@@TJvStatusBar.Create
Summary
  Creates and initializes a new TJvStatusBar object.
Description
  Use Create to create and initialize a new TJvStatusBar object.
  
  Create calls the inherited Create method, then sets the initial values for the status bar as follows: 

  * HintColor is set to clInfoBk.
  * csAcceptsControls is added to ControlStyle.
Parameters
  AOwner - A component, typically the form, that is responsible for freeing the status bar.
See Also
  HintColor
