@@TJvStatusBar.OnMouseLeave
Summary
  Occurs when the mouse pointer moves off the status bar.
Description
  Write an OnMouseLeave event handler to take specific action when the user moves the mouse off the
  status bar. For example, you can use this event to undo changes that were made in an OnMouseEnter
  event handler.
See Also
  OnMouseEnter
